Hello World if you see this commercial come across your feed don’t worry it’s just a amazing new premier of our latest influencer campaign created here at TravisLoveArt agency for the world renowned Toyota brand. This process was so much fun! It was such an honor being recognized by Toyota and chosen to create a captivating campaign with my team. This opportunity allowed me to not only showcase scripting, storyboarding and more, but I also got a chance to star in a commercial and use my very own music as well. A side of my art I don’t share often. I hope you guys enjoy! See more at TravisLove.com

Explore this exclusive “Living Artist” interview featuring the versatile creative, Travis Love. Dive into his narrative of navigating the vibrant creative scene in Atlanta during his formative years, and witness his transformative journey as he ascends to new peaks as both a designer and artist. Uncover the essence of #travisloveart, embrace the intricacies of #tanglism, and join the narrative that seamlessly weaves between the artistic landscapes of Atlanta and world wide!

During my recent visit to Houston’s art district, I stumbled upon one of the city’s hidden gems a magnificent space dedicated exclusively to artists and creatives. This hidden gem boasts pristine white wall studios and expansive galleries, providing a haven for artists seeking a space to cultivate their craft. The experience was enriched by engaging conversations with fellow artists, leading to the discovery of a vibrant and supportive community. For an immersive glimpse into this artistic haven, venture to YouTube.com/TravisloveArt and witness the full video as I explore the enchanting Winter’s Street Studio.

The yellow, like a burst of energy, breathes life into the canvas, while the profound blacks add depth and intrigue. Each stroke is a deliberate dance, capturing the essence of light and shadow in a harmonious embrace. 🌗#travisloveart
